pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: publications.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: CaSE Laboratory
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:
    - styles.css
  toc: false
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: source
  theme: flatly
  pagetitle: Publications | CaSE Lab @ CWRU
  listing:
    - id: articles
      contents: publications/*/**.qmd
      template: ./ejs/article.ejs
      categories: true
      sort:
        - year desc
        - title
      sort-ui:
        - title
        - author
        - publication
        - year
      filter-ui:
        - title
        - author
        - publication
        - year
      page-size: 10
      field-display-names:
        publication: Publication
        year: Year

Watching files for changes
Browse at http://localhost:3533/publications.html
